Cam::

She tranformed into fox mode and ran down the hall. "Hey Blackfang, 
I'm coming too. I wanna see what's goin on."  She ran at full speed, 
and to the doorway of the CR chamber. She saw a big bot infront of 
KitKat and KitKat bend over on one knee.  She saw Kup and Windlord 
and other bots she couldn't remember thier names. She raised her hand 
and yelled in a high pitched yell at the top of her voice. "CAN I 
PLAY TOO!?!"
